{
  "stem": "1537.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, he comes to me, to my bed, and they want to take me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I said, in German, to them, I work, you know, in the other side of the emergency room, with the doctors.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says he has orders to take me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I'm panicky, and I said to the other boys there who are also working, I said, do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Run-- it was 2 o'clock in the morning-- run across, you had to get out to the street to go to the other end of the block, you know, because the entrance was from the other side.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Wake up Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Thomas Martinez.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Wake him up and tell him what's happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He woke up, he run, and he gave the orders for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't touch him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He works here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So because he gave them the order, and that's the way they left me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would be-- so I don't know if it's because I saw what was going on, or he made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing is, that's the way I found out that there's 700 people were pushed into the water, with the head-- they  kept them two minutes like this, two or three guys.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when they was dead, they just threw them out of the window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the end of the 700 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the liquidation before, because they knew, probably, the war is coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only thing we know, the bombardment every day, twice a day. 11 o'clock in the morning, 11 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- so, I'm sorry, I had to go back, because I didn't want to miss this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's OK, that's fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
